Title: Dynamics AX TeamCity Build Automation
Description: Continuous Integration, Building, and Deployment hooks for Dynamics AX 2012 and JetBrain's TeamCity platform.  Works with on-prem TFS or VisualStudio Online!
HomeWiki:
Dynamics AX TeamCity Build Automation

This project is a freely-to-distribute set of scripts and accompanying AX Model to facilitate the automated building and deployment of modelstores in Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012.

The installer is located under the Downloads section as is the ReadMe file.
